 :tx/rationale "CE-OBSERVE-INSIGHT: The dialogue must be continuous, not periodic. Currently observation and hypothesis generation are DECOUPLED — 21 observations get 21 'recorded +9 datoms' responses with zero contextual insight. Every framework demands continuous dialogue: Freud (superego intervenes at moment of experience), Lacan (signifying chain extends at moment new signifier enters), Vygotsky (scaffolding happens IN the interaction), Popper (contradictions flagged the INSTANT they appear), Bakhtin (meaning co-constructed in utterance-response pair). FIX: Every braid observe returns not just 'recorded' but an IMMEDIATE micro-hypothesis compiled from the newly-connected knowledge state. After recording, the observe pipeline: (1) runs connect_to_existing (CE-CONN), (2) runs detect_topological_event (CE-TOPO) checking for new hubs, contradictions H1, void boundaries H2, (3) if event occurred, runs compile_micro_hypothesis (CE-STEER) generating a one-sentence Socratic question at current temperature, (4) includes micro-hypothesis in the observation response. The micro-hypothesis is recorded in the hypothesis ledger for calibration. This transforms braid from NOTEBOOK (records, 4/10) to SOCRATIC TUTOR (responds, dialogues, scaffolds, challenges, guides, 8+/10). ~60 LOC orchestration in observe pipeline calling functions CE-CONN/TOPO/STEER already define."
